track_notes: This was my descent route far better than my ascent route. The initial section uses a MTB route but you could keep to the Forest Roads. Make sure you pick-up the forest path off the Forest Road at NN 53789 01322 easily missed. Once through forest gate initially keep to faint path through ferns (summer) but instead of heading up to first summit keep to side of hill up to bealach and pick-up path at NN 54445 01838 for the summit. Trig point on summit with theodolite screw missing.
